th; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-style-span&quot; style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-style-span&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;&gt;2.持续的印象&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; hiragino=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; microsoft=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; font-size:=&quot;&quot; 16px=&quot;&quot; line-height:=&quot;&quot; 25=&quot;&quot; 6px=&quot;&quot; box-sizing:=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; important=&quot;&quot; word-wrap:=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; text-align: center; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://pm.cndesign.com/upload/works/20130729_2DE40635106842016879855.jpg&quot; _xhe_src=&quot;http://pm.cndesign.com/upload/works/20130729_2DE40635106842016879855.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; hiragino=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; microsoft=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; font-size:=&quot;&quot; 16px=&quot;&quot; line-height:=&quot;&quot; 25=&quot;&quot; 6px=&quot;&quot; box-sizing:=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; important=&quot;&quot; word-wrap:=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;	&lt;/span&gt;在最初的浏览后，用户需要一个理由让他们继续留在这里，深入地了解你的网站，公司，品牌。因此给用户更多的，让&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 25.6px;&quot;&gt;用户看到你在设计方面的与众不同。（好的视觉效果能够轻松的做到这一点。）一个漂亮的主页是非常棒的，但是你网&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 25.6px;&quot;&gt;站上的其它页面，元素和工具也应该去进行良好的设计。试想下这种情况：很可能超过半数的用户进入你的网站是通过&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; hiragino=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; microsoft=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; font-size:=&quot;&quot; 16px=&quot;&quot; line-height:=&quot;&quot; 25=&quot;&quot; 6px=&quot;&quot; box-sizing:=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; important=&quot;&quot; word-wrap:=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;&gt;其它页面而不是主页。&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; hiragino=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; microsoft=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; font-size:=&quot;&quot; 16px=&quot;&quot; line-height:=&quot;&quot; 25=&quot;&quot; 6px=&quot;&quot; box-sizing:=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; important=&quot;&quot; word-wrap:=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; hiragino=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; microsoft=&quo